---
title: Moroccan Chicken, Lentil & Veggie Stew with Mash & Flaked Almonds
description: Bring the warm Moroccan flavours to your table in the form of a stew packed on top of a blanket of mashed potato. The
comforting addition of chicken, lentils and spices is everything this stew needs to end a long day.
